parameters:
【Professor Skolan】 The amount of magical power
varies depending on the region.

【Professor Skolan】 The region of Yula, where the
Greatland Kingdom is located, is the place with
the highest concentration of magical power.

【Professor Skolan】 The reason is said to be
because the Hell Empire is located beneath the
Greatland Kingdom.

【Professor Skolan】 Therefore, the Eastern Province
where the Greatland Kingdom is located and the
Ocean Province where the United States is located
have a lower concentration of magical power.

【Professor Skolan】 Because of that, there are
fewer people becoming magicians compared to the
Yula Province.

【Professor Skolan】 There are not many instances of
demons invading, so it is a natural result.
